## ðŸš¨ Non-Negotiable Engineering Rules

- Do NOT introduce microservices during MVP.
- Do NOT couple UI logic to backend services.
- Do NOT hardcode dealer-specific workflows.
- Prefer modular, replaceable components.
- Keep services stateless when possible.
